# Mosquitto password file — generated via `mosquitto_passwd`.
# Copy to ./passwd, then create real entries with:
#
#   docker run --rm -v "$PWD/passwd:/passwd" eclipse-mosquitto:2.0.20 \
#     mosquitto_passwd -b /passwd <username> <password>
#
# Default placeholder accounts referenced by acl.example:
#   - backend-bridge       (used by the mqtt_bridge edge function)
#   - dashboard-readonly   (read-only observation account)
#   - device-<patient_id>  (one per provisioned wearable)
#
# Never commit the real passwd file; it's gitignored.
